				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-B%C3%A1-Qu%C3%A1t/Chi%E1%BA%BFt-h%E1%BA%A1m-tinh-tr%E1%BB%B1c-th%E1%BA%A7n/poem-CXhS00MnAwXRdhJRz9LKGA">Chiết hạm tinh trực thần - 折檻旌直臣</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-B%C3%A1-Qu%C3%A1t/author-2eyz08Vw3mwjAHFJik43sA">Cao Bá Quát</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/C%E1%BB%95-phong-k%E1%BB%B3-08-Thi%C3%AAn-t%C3%A2n-tam-nguy%E1%BB%87t-th%C3%AC/poem-h4Jd-rpUD9F5lc3rtXZ3WA">Cổ phong kỳ 08 (Thiên tân tam nguyệt thì) - 古風其八（天津三月時）</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/author-8WYDeeki5xZo8eD-k6Sk5A">Lý Bạch</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Ph%C3%BAc-%C6%AFng-B%C3%ACnh/%C4%90%C3%A1p-ho%E1%BA%A1-K%E1%BB%89nh-Ch%E1%BB%89-th%E1%BB%8B-Phan-V%C4%83n-Hy-hi%E1%BB%81n-h%E1%BB%AFu-k%C3%BD-ho%C3%A0i-nguy%C3%AAn-v%E1%BA%ADn/poem-5Br14d1Bv0g8uJJf_9jOSQ">Đáp hoạ Kỉnh Chỉ thị Phan Văn Hy hiền hữu ký hoài nguyên vận - 答和敬止氏潘文譆賢友寄懷原韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Ph%C3%BAc-%C6%AFng-B%C3%ACnh/author-eQ6wft6d1E9_uEITUaRRlg">Nguyễn Phúc Ưng Bình</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/H%C3%A0nh-l%E1%BA%A1c-t%E1%BB%AB-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-oD-EpfnwjX41EI6znPIV2g">Hành lạc từ kỳ 2 - 行樂詞其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/author-ZRyB2U-4oqfhcjZ7xrf1_A">Nguyễn Du</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/H%E1%BB%89-v%C4%83n-quan-qu%C3%A2n-d%C4%A9-l%C3%A2m-t%E1%BA%B7c-c%E1%BA%A3nh-nh%E1%BB%8B-th%E1%BA%ADp-v%E1%BA%ADn/poem--7aSmm5Sn3I7FvPVGG4inQ">Hỉ văn quan quân dĩ lâm tặc cảnh, nhị thập vận - 喜聞官軍已臨賊境二十韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%A3-%C3%94n/L%C6%B0u-Lang-ph%E1%BB%91-kh%E1%BA%A9u-h%C3%A0o/poem-GVXMYzCs5aGxhI9Ocqqwwg">Lưu Lang phố khẩu hào - 劉郎浦口號</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%A3-%C3%94n/author-_UcTlQEkv8W7QwNFexN15A">Lã Ôn</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Quang-B%E1%BA%ADt/Ph%E1%BB%A5ng-ho%E1%BA%A1-ng%E1%BB%B1-ch%E1%BA%BF-Mai-hoa/poem-r0X22jqT9P_WO2h0MRIHOA">Phụng hoạ ngự chế “Mai hoa” - 奉和御製梅花</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Quang-B%E1%BA%ADt/author-uKsiCb0CAnZcZT9U9On7LQ">Nguyễn Quang Bật</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%E1%BB%AB-Trung-H%C3%A0nh/S%C6%A1n-L%C4%83ng-%C4%91%E1%BA%A1o-trung-phong-v%C5%A9/poem-gD0FrXD6P5xRUsqPInUdkQ">Sơn Lăng đạo trung phong vũ - 山陵道中風雨</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%E1%BB%AB-Trung-H%C3%A0nh/author-aUZNU7wtOFuw7SBMW9XW1Q">Từ Trung Hành</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Khuy%E1%BA%BFt-danh-Vi%E1%BB%87t-Nam/Thang-b%C3%A0n-ph%C3%BA/poem-zRWhSi8OLsCDGbk659PgVA">Thang bàn phú - 湯盤賦</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Khuy%E1%BA%BFt-danh-Vi%E1%BB%87t-Nam/author-kBTBt5Mbi6PPrH2sJkQAPw">Khuyết danh Việt Nam</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/V%E1%BB%8Bnh-Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-H%C3%A1n-Si%C3%AAu/poem-eJQPVwiQY02pZj5Ee17GJw">Vịnh Trương Hán Siêu - 詠張漢超</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/author-JHbQVfC53E2lRJL-xE616A">Nguyễn Khuyến</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
